  "frame_eqs": "timepeak = if(equal(time%0.1, 0),timepeak=timepeak+1.1/fps, timepeak); //the timepeak variable increases using the time variable in sync\ntimepeak2 = if(equal(time%0.1, 0),timepeak2=timepeak2+1.1/fps, timepeak2); //another one, but the same thing; both time sync now uses fps-independent algorithm. Thank you, Nitorami (martin)! Recommended BPM: around 120 BPM.\n\n/////////////TRIGGER OPTION////////////////\n\n//Simple Bass Trigger//\n//timepeak = if(above(bass, 1.74),timepeak=0, timepeak);\n\n//Bass Trigger with Delay//\nbassdelay = timepeak>0.5;\nbeatdelaytrigger = if(bassdelay, if(above(bass, 1.74), timepeak=0, timepeak), bleh);\n\n\n//RANDOM POSITION BEAT TRIGGER (FINALLY WORKING)//\nwave_x = wavexrand;\nbasswavextrigger = if(bassdelay, if(above(bass, 1.74), wavexrand=rand(0.3), wavexrand), wavexrand);\nwave_y = waveyrand;\nbasswaveytrigger = if(bassdelay, if(above(bass, 1.74), waveyrand=rand(0.3), waveyrand), waveyrand);\nwave_mystery = wavemysteryrand;\nbasswavemysterytrigger = if(bassdelay, if(above(bass, 1.74), wavemysteryrand=rand(1), wavemysteryrand), wavemysteryrand);\n\n//Another Bass Trigger with Delay + count feature//\nbassdelay2 = timepeak2>1;\nbeatdelaytrigger2 = if(bassdelay2, if(above(bass, 1.74), timepeak2=0, timepeak2), bleh);\n\ncount = if(bassdelay2, if(above(bass, 1.74), count=count+1, count), count);\ncount = if(count%8==0, count=0, count); //it resets to 0 if it passes to 8;\n\nwave_a=100;\nwave_r = 0.01 + mid_att/18;\nq1 = count;\nmonitor = count+1;\n\ncount = if(above(timepeak, 1.87), -1, count);\n\n//Suitable for 100-125 BPM songs!\n//Written by Incubo_",
